message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.NE. The paper discusses a new open domain question answering task that involves generating semi-structured assertions from a passage and a question. This task involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
